{"tid":393101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港眾志稱網頁被黑客入侵　被修改為愛國內容","createTime":"2017-09-09T03:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T04:32:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"554adef04664c88e00aa0d43ae701e4235a1334f","tid":393101,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T03:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1353162_1_L_20170909114814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1353162_1_L_20170909114814.jpg&h=f56085a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港眾志表示，網頁被黑客入侵，網站頁面被修改為愛國內容，現時正在修復中。記者嘗試登入香港眾志網頁，顯示為無法連結。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志表示，過去經常受到有組織的黑客攻擊，譴責有關黑客杜撰香港眾志成員支持釋法的行為。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志批評行為屬於幼稚的民族主義操作，重申人大強行釋法，取消民選議員資格，是剝奪超過18萬選民選舉權利，令香港步向三權合作的威權體制。"},{"pid":"c3be64c820ccfda07612a2c64a7012287d17c232","tid":393101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"咁渣架<br />\n<br />\nPASSWORD用chifung1234?"},{"pid":"bc05605374526ae4cc65fbb12d777f90396b731d","tid":393101,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99fe68a1a37be827be19ec9411baa4af9cfb56f2","tid":393101,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"又leak哂重要資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee333087385572cfab006176c469c31feadd51de","tid":393101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又leak哂重要資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉...眾志班天才..."}]}